column5: Headed out yesterday, with 2 buddies to see if we could find the crappies again. Real tough bite,but we plugged along all day and slowly picked up a crappie here , a crappie there.(no big cocentration) By the end of the day,we had boated over 60,with a few SLABS.
Beauty SLABS Larry   I foresee stir fry in your future
you're holding it like winning bingo tickets
Crappies like elephant ears. Very nice!

I was so happy to see a bunch of fish in the 10-12" range this weekend. But damn those things are slabs!  And good idea to run to the main lake to take pictures lol. I took my pictures in another spot as well.
Awesome shot of some serious slabs....way to go!
